promptResultCard.createPromptDescription: Open "Edit Prompt" and write your prompt or paste sections of other prompts.
promptResultCard.fillFormGenerateContent: Begin by filling out the prompt template inputs using natural language. Once you filled in the prompt template, select the "Generate" button.
Fill the Form and Generate Content
promptResultCard.generateContentDescript: If you've created input fields fill them in and select "Generate". Adobe's generative AI will process your input and generate unique content based on your specifications.
promptResultCard.refineContentDescriptio: After content is generated if you want to refine it further, update the prompt and / or input fields. Once you are happy with the content leverage in your AEM authoring experience.
promptResultCard.savePromptDescription: If you want to reuse the prompt created select "Save".  This allows you to store the prompt for future use. You can save it at the user or organization level.
